Install kickstarter from https://meego.gitorious.org/meego-developer-tools/kickstarter

$ git clone git://gitorious.org/meego-developer-tools/kickstarter.git
$ cd kickstarter
$ make
$ sudo python ./setup.py

More information can be found from: https://meego.gitorious.org/meego-developer-tools/kickstarter/blobs/master/README

Updating .ks files

$ kickstarter -c configurations.yaml -r repos.yaml
